outputs.output_descr: To define the unifying framework for ensuring economic growth, weath creation and socio-political transformation of Liberia over the next 18 years.

project_descr: Conflict Sensitive National Long Term Vision for Sustainable Development and Economic Growth Strategy project defines the unifying framework for socio economic transformation via analysis, scenario constructions, consultations and growth diagnosis.
project_title: National Long Term Vision and Economic Growth Strategy
